Name: AppId
Description: The appId that is associated with this marketing event. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: Attendees
Description: The number of people who attended this marketing event

Name: Cancellations
Description: The number of cancellations for this marketing event

Name: Created by user ID
Description: The user that created this object. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: Object create date/time
Description: The date and time at which this object was created. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: End date
Description: The end date and time of the marketing event.

Name: Cancelled
Description: Indicates if the marketing event has been cancelled.

Name: Description
Description: The description of the marketing event

Name: Event Finished
Description: Indicates if the marketing event has been finished.

Name: Name
Description: The name of the event

Name: Organizer
Description: The marketing event organizer

Name: Type
Description: The type of marketing event

Name: Url
Description: The url to the marketing event

Name: Import status
Description: Stores last import status associated with MarketingEvent

Name: Object last modified date/time
Description: Most recent timestamp of any property update for this object. This includes HubSpot internal properties, which can be visible or hidden. This property is updated automatically.

Name: Merged record IDs
Description: The list of record IDs that have been merged into this record. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: No shows
Description: The number of people who registered for this marketing event but did not attend nor cancel

Name: Record ID
Description: The unique ID for this record. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: Record Source Detail 1
Description: First level of detail on how this record was created

Name: Record Source Detail 2
Description: Second level of detail on how this record was created

Name: Record Source Detail 3
Description: Third level of detail on how this record was created

Name: Record Source
Description: How this record was created

Name: Registrations
Description: The current number of registrations for this marketing event

Name: Start date
Description: The start date and time of the marketing event.

Name: Updated by user ID
Description: The user that last updated this object. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: Owner Assigned Date
Description: The most recent date an owner was assigned to this object. This is set automatically by HubSpot and can be used for segmentation and reporting.

Name: Owner
Description: The owner of the object.

Name: HubSpot Team
Description: The primary team of the owner.
